Package net.minecraftforge.client.model.geometry

Interface IModelGeometry<T extends IModelGeometry<T>>

All Known Subinterfaces:
IMultipartModelGeometry<T>, ISimpleModelGeometry<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
CompositeModel.Geometry, DynamicBucketModel, FluidModel, ItemLayerModel, ModelLoaderRegistry.VanillaProxy, MultiLayerModel, NewModelLoaderTest.TestModel, OBJModel, SeparatePerspectiveModel
public interface IModelGeometry<T extends IModelGeometry<T>>
General interface for any model that can be baked, superset of vanilla IUnbakedModel. Models can be baked to different vertex formats and with different state.
